quotes.Num1: Success is not final; failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts.
quotes.Num2: It is better to fail in originality than to succeed in imitation.
quotes.Num3: The road to success and the road to failure are almost exactly the same.
quotes.Num4: Success usually comes to those who are too busy to be looking for it.
quotes.Num5: Develop success from failures. Discouragement and failure are two of the surest stepping stones to success.
